Title: IRC<->Discord Relay
Description: A customisable chat relay that relays between an IRC channel and a Discord channel.

Title: Jewelraid
Description: A Minetest mod that adds a game where each team has to steal jewels from the other team to not loose.

Title: JMute
Description: A Minetest mod that adds the ability to temporarily/permanently mute players.

Title: Time Stone
Description: A Minetest Mod that adds stones that can change the time.

Title: Teleport Carrot
Description: A Minetest mod that adds an item that has a chance of teleporting you somewhere nearby.

Title: Protective Shell
Description: A Dragonfire client CSM that makes a barrier around you.

Title: Keystrokes
Description: A Minetest CSM that adds the ability to see which keys/buttons are being pressed.

Title: Sumo Duels
Description: A Minetest mod that implements the sumo duels minigame.

Title: Barrier Redo
Description: A fork of the Minetest barrier mod with an extra feature.

Title: Tag
Description: A Minetest mod that adds the ability to play tag.

Title: Biome Detector
Description: A minetest mod that allows you to get the name of the biome you are in.
